Project Overview
This is a multi-page website created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
The project demonstrates web design skills by incorporating:

Navigation Menu with Icons

Responsive Hero Sections

Embedded Video

Images, Lists, and Tables

External JavaScript file with Functions

Custom Designed Logo and Icons

ğŸ“¥ How to Open the Project in IntelliJ IDEA
Open IntelliJ IDEA.

Click File > New > Project from Existing Sources.

Navigate to your project folder where you saved all your files (Home.html, AboutUs.html, FAQ.html, Contact.html, all CSS, JS, Images, Videos).

Select the project folder and click OK.

In IntelliJ IDEA:

Right-click on Home.html â†’ Select Open in Browser â†’ Choose your browser (e.g., Chrome, Firefox).

If the browser icon does not appear:

Go to File > Settings > Plugins

Search for "JavaScript and HTML" plugins and install them.

Restart IntelliJ and try again.

