ğŸ”¥ Important Notes
Do not rename the folders like images/ and videos/.

All paths must remain relative (e.g., images/aboutus.jpg).

Make sure your video (aivideo.mp4) is inside the videos/ folder.

To test JavaScript functions (e.g., greeting pop-up or scroll buttons), make sure myScript.js is correctly linked in each HTML page.

